// barstate.* are per-bar booleans, and the flags behind them follow from where
// a bar sits in the series rather than being set by hand.
//
// This runs on the last of the loaded bars, so it is the last bar and not the
// first. Every bar of a completed series is closed history, and none of it is
// real time.
log.info(barstate.isfirst)
log.info(barstate.islast)
log.info(barstate.isnew)
log.info(barstate.isconfirmed)
log.info(barstate.ishistory)
log.info(barstate.isrealtime)
log.info(barstate.islastconfirmedhistory)

// Expected output:
// false
// true
// true
// true
// true
// false
// true
